Pounds 114.9m.
Interest payable was cut by 56 per cent to Pounds 1.1m (Pounds 2.54m) and
there were exceptional costs of Pounds 1.6m relating mainly to the closure
of Harkwell Labels &amp; Tags. Extraordinary charges of Pounds 1.14m derived
from the disposal of non-core businesses.
Earnings emerged at 13.5p (22.7p) per share and the directors have proposed
holding the final dividend at 8.25p for a maintained 12.5p total.
