companies.
Turnover advanced 3 per cent to Pounds 16.2m (Pounds 15.7m). Earnings per
share were 3.9p (5p) but the interim dividend has been maintained at 1.75p.
There was an extraordinary credit of Pounds 1.58m from the sale of the Duke
of York's Theatre.
